'''Tenjinyama Kofun''' (天神山古墳) refers to various {{ill|kofun|ja|古墳|1=Kofun|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/kofun|13=User:Immanuelle/Kofun|qq=}} (ancient Kofuns) in Japan.
Due to the large number of kofun sharing this name, they are often referred to by appending their respective locations.
